// Solution Section - The system
---

<section id="the-system" class="bg-brand-gray py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24">
  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-12 text-center">
        The system.
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-2 bg-brand-accent rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-2">Daily async check-ins.</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-muted">Not calls. Not forms. Quick back-and-forth, same way you already run your team.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-2 bg-brand-accent rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-2">Pattern tracking.</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-muted">I track compliance, excuses, trends. The stuff you'd never catch yourself.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-2 bg-brand-accent rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-2">Done-for-you nutrition.</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-muted">Meals planned. No decision fatigue.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-2 bg-brand-accent rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-2">Training in an app.</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-muted">1-hour workouts. Show up, execute, done.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-2 bg-brand-accent rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-2">Weekly strategy call.</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-muted">Adjustments, obstacles, what's next.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-brand-text font-semibold text-center mt-12">
        You delegate everything else. This is delegating your health to someone who won't let you off the hook.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
